  <brief_title>Effect of Different Injection Speeds for Spinal Anaesthesia in Caesarean Section</brief_title>
  <official_title>Injection Speed of Spinal Anaesthesia for Asian Women Undergoing Lower Segmental Caesarean Section and the Incidence of Hypotension and/or Use of Vasopressors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
